Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是梦…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.61,0:02:01.71,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好大的雨
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶 是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里是…哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.61,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好不容易抓到的蝙蝠都逃走了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.02,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君真是的 别哭了啦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种东西马上就能抓到的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.00,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是啊 别哭哭啼啼的了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本大爷我会给你抓来的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.36,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来你在这种地方
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.38,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快过来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.29,0:04:22.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个人 是刚才在庭院里的…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君 我们走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.12,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 你该回去学习了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…我才不要
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之前我不是一直都在学习吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.51,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不想听借口
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快回房间去
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.66,0:04:48.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人和礼人都在玩 为什么只有我要去学习呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.02,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你和其他的孩子不一样
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要 我还想玩
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要我说几遍你才明白
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.74,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可是继承人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你明白那意味着什么吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.88,0:05:04.59,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来 说说看你该怎么做
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.35,0:05:13.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要成为…第一
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能输给…任何人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你没能做到呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.93,0:05:27.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就不是妈妈的孩子 要被沉到湖底
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 真是乖孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.21,0:05:36.03,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是第一的话 你就没有任何价值
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.51,0:05:37.75,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那样的孩子啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.82,0:05:47.82,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就要永远孤独地生活在冰冷的湖底 没有人会来救你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不想那样的话 就给我回房去
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.28,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母亲大人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人 我的小金丝雀 歌唱吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为我唱那首歌
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的 母亲大人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个长得很漂亮的人是…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.50,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君他们的…妈妈吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.41,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.50,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是 怜司君？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.23,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.41,0:07:11.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快看 这是我朋友刚才送给我的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快把它放下
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.61,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好痒
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.97,0:07:23.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是家中的长子 是要成为下任家主的人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论在什么时候 你都必须要有长子的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要干什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.00,0:07:41.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.22,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和埃德加约好要好好照顾它的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.13,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母亲大人 这本书的内容我全都记住了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.43,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.39,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.57,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个人是…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}科迪莉亚
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个世上最美丽的人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.58,0:09:41.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世间万物都爱慕着你
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.08,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣服在你的面前
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里希特
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.89,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要永远待在我的身边 向我轻诉爱语
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.15,0:10:01.95,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.75,0:10:41.26,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 醒醒
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人…君 这里是？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.81,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下水道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.45,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.67,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下雨的时候不要靠近这里
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那扇门是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不必知道
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.53,0:11:14.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的手怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶 是在哪里被划伤了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.41,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是甜美的香气啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是所谓的「魅惑之香」吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们就在这里一起玩吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.87,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}确实是香气馥郁
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总觉得好像在哪里闻到过
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么 要做这种事
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.98,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你问我为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然是因为好玩啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.28,0:11:55.88,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让开
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一样的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.12,0:12:16.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}心脏 又…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.36,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.87,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绫人君 你这样就够了？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.86,0:12:30.03,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那差不多是时候让我来享用了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.74,0:12:31.99,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}随你的便
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 我就开动了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.18,0:12:37.84,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没用的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你已经无法从我身边逃离了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.36,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝴蝶啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.58,0:12:52.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}越是挣扎就越会被束缚在蜘蛛的网中
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.99,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会好好疼爱你的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.13,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就乖乖别动
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我喜欢你 小贱人
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}切 我腻了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.97,0:13:31.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}够了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.79,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嫉妒是最棒的香料
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.75,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遭受掠夺也不算坏
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.09,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}越是憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.80,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就爱得越深
